On OS X, all can be installed with MacPorts
On Linux, use appropriate package management

First install Ruby 1.9.2, Perl 5.12, GSL, and gnuplot with MacPorts / package management:

sudo port install ruby19 perl5 gnuplot gsl

Then install Bundler with Gem:

sudo gem1.9 install bundler

The use bundler to install the rest of the requirements:

bundle install